2026-03-29T13:35:50.3794179Z               "message": "Integrate unreachable device display into battery/device status section\n\nPoll zigbee_connectivity API alongside battery readings, store status per\ndevice, and surface unreachable devices in both the daily summary email\nand admin detail page. The device status section now shows when any\nbattery is low OR any device is unreachable.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01N2A7MASDjYVWA5SWYBa7rP",
