2026-03-29T13:35:50.3800561Z               "id": "1dc6537907d0bae5cba7367e8e9d167f9a52e4c6",
2026-03-29T13:35:50.3801817Z               "message": "Add diagnostic script for Hue zigbee connectivity API\n\nBash script that calls the Hue CLIP v2 API to fetch devices,\nzigbee_connectivity, and device_power resources, then cross-references\nowner.rid mappings to help diagnose unreachable device display issues.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01N2A7MASDjYVWA5SWYBa7rP",
2026-03-29T13:35:50.3803067Z               "timestamp": "2026-03-29T11:28:35Z",
