2026-03-29T13:35:50.3808093Z               "id": "dfe3627c16d870eb86f28b65f8e21c5e3e811b4b",
2026-03-29T13:35:50.3809693Z               "message": "Fix early return in LoadBatteryStatusAsync skipping connectivity query\n\nThe method returned early when no battery-type devices existed in the DB,\nwhich also skipped the unreachable device connectivity query below it.\nWrap battery processing in a conditional block instead so connectivity\nis always checked.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01N2A7MASDjYVWA5SWYBa7rP",
2026-03-29T13:35:50.3811145Z               "timestamp": "2026-03-29T11:40:37Z",
