2026-03-29T13:35:50.3858501Z               "message": "Add coverage tests for device type derivation, connectivity, and zigbee API\n\n- PollingServiceTests: temperature-only device type, stale removal guard\n  on non-battery cycles, device type update on existing devices\n- HueApiClientTests: GetZigbeeConnectivityAsync endpoint and deserialization\n- DetailModelTests: unreachable device loading, connectivity JSON error\n  handling, connected device filtering, null window offset fallback\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01Gmjk912cuixJo7D9UqZQGA",
