2026-03-29T13:35:50.3870246Z               "message": "Show all battery info in Device Status section, connectivity issues first\n\n- Always show battery statuses when the Device Status section is rendered,\n  not just when batteries are below the alert threshold\n- Render connectivity issues before battery statuses in both email and admin\n- Sort battery by level then name, connectivity alphabetically by name\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01Gmjk912cuixJo7D9UqZQGA",
